Using Interquartile Range(IQR)¶

  • H-Spread/Mid_spread
  • Measures the statistical dispersion/spread
  • IQR = Quantile 3(75) - Quantile 1(25)
In [111]:
q1 = df.quantile(0.25)
q3 = df.quantile(0.75)
In [112]:
IQR = q3 - q1

df_no_outlier = df[~((df < (q1 -1.5 * IQR)) | (df >(q3 + 1.5 * IQR))).any(axis=1)]
